00:02:17.470 --> 00:02:20.140  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
Damn it. You mean
we have to just sit here

8
00:02:20.223 --> 00:02:22.058  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
and watch Pyunma race
for his life?

9
00:02:22.225 --> 00:02:23.726  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
For the moment, we just need

10
00:02:23.810 --> 00:02:26.312  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
to put all our trust in him
and not interfere.

11
